      "7": "For|strong=\"G1063\"the|strong=\"G3588\"overseer|strong=\"G1985\"must|strong=\"G1163\"be|strong=\"G1510\"blameless, as|strong=\"G5613\"God|strong=\"G2316\"’s steward|strong=\"G3623\", not|strong=\"G3361\"self-pleasing, not|strong=\"G3361\"easily angered, not|strong=\"G3361\"given|strong=\"G3361\"to|strong=\"G1163\"wine|strong=\"G3943\", not|strong=\"G3361\"violent|strong=\"G4131\", not|strong=\"G3361\"greedy for|strong=\"G1063\"dishonest gain;",
